The programm need to environnement variable:
OGL_VPL_PROJ: the root of the project, actually it's where file main.cpp is.
SDL_PATH: the main folder of the sdl librairie.
ASSIMP_PATH : the main folder of the assimp libary need for load 3D model
DEVIL_PATH : the main folder of the developper image library need for load different image formats (png,jpg,tga)
GLM_PATH : the main folder for the openGL mathematics library